---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Melloware — supporting the open source community since 1999.">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <p>
    Melloware was established in 1999 as a platform to house our applications that addressed gaps
    we identified in the market. We believe our software is both innovative and practical,
    fulfilling needs that we felt should have been addressed by others but weren't!
  </p>

  <h3>Our Motto</h3>

  <blockquote>
    <p>
      "The most successful method of programming is to begin a program as simply as possible,
      test it, and then add to the program until it performs the required job."
    </p>
    <footer>— PDP8 handbook, Pg9-64</footer>
  </blockquote>

  <h3>Connect</h3>

  <ul class="links">
    <li><a href="https://github.com/melloware">GitHub</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/users/502366/melloware">Stack Overflow</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/emillefkof/">LinkedIn</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/sponsors/melloware">Sponsor on GitHub</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.paypal.me/mellowareinc">Donate via PayPal</a></li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  blockquote footer {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .links li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
